./sdp/logs/Lead_T-013_20260425T183959Za_1777156511.log:3002:my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-humanization.md:39:**Phase 3 — Memory, silence, ensemble (CCH-022..CCH-029).** R9 Motif memory with LRU + variation menu + return-home decay. R10 Silence budgets with wind-voice lung-capacity caps. R11 Call-response gating. Section-level envelope compositing. Tempo-dependent swing (Friberg/Sundström). Arc-shape variety. Restraint as global dampener. End-of-phase: 5-minute generative pieces no longer feel looped; repetition-variance metrics pass thresholds.
./sdp/logs/Lead_T-013_20260425T183959Za_1777156511.log:3006:my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-sampler.md:29:**In scope:** a granular SuperCollider voice (`sw_sampler`) with a dedicated effects bus; a sample library on disk with tag-based selection; a continuous live-capture daemon for contact/room mics; a self-quotation loop; integration with the existing artist-mode selector and cast planner so the sampler joins the signature quintet; metrics and anti-pattern detection for sampler over- or under-use.
./sdp/logs/Lead_T-013_20260425T183959Za_1777156511.log:3009:my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-sampler.md:50:**Phase 5 — Verification + observability (CCS-029..CCS-033).** Per-piece sampler-event metrics; anti-pattern detection for sampler dominating (over-quote) or never appearing (silent quintet member); a sample-usage journal that records which samples played in which pieces with what transformations; end-to-end smoke test on cypherclaw confirming the daemon is capturing, the selector is choosing, the synth is playing, and the self-listener is observing the right output peaks. End of phase: composer can demonstrate a piece that uses 1 self-quotation + 1 room-capture + 1 library sample, all selector-chosen, all routed through the effects bus, all surfaced in the diagnostics dashboard.
./sdp/logs/Lead_T-013_20260425T183959Za_1777156511.log:3010:my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-sampler.md:55:- `my-claw/tools/senseweave/artist_identity.py` — Mode-driven voice/tempo/density. `SIGNATURE_VOICES` extends from quartet to quintet; modes specify per-mode sampler density.
./sdp/logs/Lead_T-013_20260425T183959Za_1777156511.log:3011:my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-sampler.md:94:| CCS-006 | Add `sw_sampler` to `SIGNATURE_VOICES` quintet in `artist_identity.py` and update `VOICE_ROLES` so a `"sampler"` role maps to `"sw_sampler"`. | MUST | T1 | - `SIGNATURE_VOICES` becomes `("sw_bell_warm", "sw_bowed", "sw_breath", "sw_pad", "sw_sampler")`<br/>- `VOICE_ROLES["sampler"] = "sw_sampler"`<br/>- existing `VOICE_ROLES` keys for melody/counter/color/texture/bass unchanged<br/>- existing `test_artist_identity.py::TestSignatureVoices::test_quartet_size` is renamed to `test_quintet_size` and asserts length 5; quartet-specific assertions migrated |
