+## T-021 (2026-05-23)
+
+- **Exploration findings:** The active tracker timing surface is
+  `my-claw/tools/senseweave/music_tracker.py`, with runtime conversion in
+  `my-claw/tools/senseweave/music_tracker_runtime.py` and coverage in
